OL,3,CTennis player and trials motorcyclist
OL,4,Ctake top Isle of Man sports awards
OL,6,FTennis player Billy Harris and
OL,7,Fmotorcycle trials star Kaytlyn Adshead
OL,8,Fhave taken the top honours at the Isle
OL,9,Fof Man Sports Awards.
OL,11,FHarris has been named sportsman of the
OL,12,Fyear at the awards after enjoying a
OL,13,Flandmark year.
OL,15,FHis first Wimbledon victory, a maiden
OL,16,FATP Challenger Tour title in France,
OL,17,Fearning him a career-high ranking of
OL,18,F101, before being selected to
OL,19,Frepresent Great Britain in the Davis
OL,20,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
