PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772204159
OL,3,CTennis player and trials motorcyclist
OL,4,Ctake top Isle of Man sports awards
OL,6,FAdshead was named sportswoman of the
OL,7,Fyear, after becoming the first Manx
OL,8,Fwoman to secure a European title in
OL,9,Fmotorcycle trials, and also finished
OL,10,Ffourth in the Women's World
OL,11,FChampionship.
OL,13,FThe annual awards ceremony was held at
OL,14,Fthe Villa Marina on Thursday 26
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FCyclist Becky Storrie and TT sidecar
OL,18,Fracers Ryan and Callum Crowe were also
OL,19,Famong the other winners at the awards,
OL,20,Fpicking up the Ambassador and Team of
OL,21,Fthe Year prizes respectively.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
