FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772204159
OL,3,CTennis player and trials motorcyclist
OL,4,Ctake top Isle of Man sports awards
OL,6,FThe next generation of island talent
OL,7,Fwas celebrated, with athlete Regan
OL,8,FCorrin and hockey star Sienna Dunn
OL,9,Fclaiming the Under-21 awards, and para
OL,10,Fpowerlifting star Alfie Bezance
OL,11,Fwinning Disability Sportsperson of the
OL,12,FYear.
OL,14,FLes Callow received the Lifetime
OL,15,FAchievement Award for his contribution
OL,16,Fto squash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
