PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772204159
OL,3,CTennis player and trials motorcyclist
OL,4,Ctake top Isle of Man sports awards
OL,6,FDaphne Caine MHK, Minister for
OL,7,FEducation, Sport and Culture, said:
OL,8,F"The Isle of Man Sports Awards are a
OL,9,Fcelebration not only of exceptional
OL,10,Ftalent, but of the dedication,
OL,11,Fresilience and community spirit that
OL,12,Fdefine Manx sport.
OL,14,F"Every nominee and winner should be
OL,15,Fimmensely proud of what they have
OL,16,Faccomplished. As a Government, we
OL,17,Fremain committed to supporting sport
OL,18,Fat all levels, helping more people to
OL,19,Fparticipate, develop and achieve their
OL,20,Fpotential."
